We recommended that management:
create data bank of information of all indigents per barangay, through the Social Workers Office, for ready reference in processing financial assistance and other related transactions.;
study the flow of the transaction documents from inception, processing, authorization and payment of financial assistance and based thereon, set up clear-cut policies and guidelines on its program of granting financial assistances, donations and other form of assistances which will be in line with DSWD MC No. 2014-002;
define the qualifications of the beneficiaries, amounts to be given, and the processing office to ensure that only qualified beneficiaries are assisted and that the assistance is given only for public and general welfare purposes.
